Reformation Month

This web app allows users to participate in reading challenges, track the number of chapters they've read, track chapters for others, as well as create family-groups and 
there own reading challenge.

Tech stack

This uses a React.js frontend with some bootstrap for styling. The webapp runs on an Express server in a Nodejs environmnet. User profiles are stored on a
PostgreSQL database. The project is hosted on Heroku.

It's free to sign-up, and only requires an email and password.
